#

Maple Mustard Pork Tenderloin

40 min
$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasySavorySweet

Description

A savory-sweet dish featuring tender pork coated in a maple mustard glaze, perfect for a weeknight dinner.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1.5 pounds
  • maple syrup: 1/4 cup
  • dijon mustard: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic cloves: 2, minced
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
